## How Skills Work

### 1. Automatic Discovery

**When Cursor starts:**
- Scans `.cursor/skills/` directory
- Reads `SKILL.md` files
- Extracts skill names and descriptions
- Makes skills available to Agent

**Agent sees:**
- Skill names
- Skill descriptions
- Decides relevance based on your request

### 2. Dynamic Loading

**When Agent decides a skill is relevant:**
- Loads full `SKILL.md` content
- Reads supporting files (`examples/`, `references/`, `scripts/`)
- Uses skill instructions to perform task
- Only loads when needed (efficient context usage)

**Result:** ~47% token reduction vs loading all skills upfront

